      "id": "PopularPost172062",
      "post_content": "Hope they don't attack with creatures that have two or greater power. Otherwise, this expensive card would be only slowing your inevitable demise. Even in multiplayer, this card comes down too late and doesn't scale well against the size of the average creature in the format.\n  \n   \nI understand that you can nullify pretty much all combat damage with Righteous Cause in conjunction with Humility. However, there are plenty of cheaper cards that can do just the same: [Watchdog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Watchdog), [Weakstone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Weakstone), [Juntu Stakes](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Juntu Stakes), [Caltrops](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Caltrops), [Thunderstaff](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thunderstaff).",
      "posted_by": "scumbling1",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost172062\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Hope they don't attack with creatures that have two or greater power. Otherwise, this expensive card would be only slowing your inevitable demise. Even in multiplayer, this card comes down too late and doesn't scale well against the size of the average creature in the format.\r<br/> <br/>I understand that you can nullify pretty much all combat damage with Righteous Cause in conjunction with Humility. However, there are plenty of cheaper cards that can do just the same: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Watchdog\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Watchdog\">Watchdog</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Weakstone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Weakstone\">Weakstone</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Juntu Stakes\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Juntu Stakes\">Juntu Stakes</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Caltrops\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Caltrops\">Caltrops</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thunderstaff\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thunderstaff\">Thunderstaff</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '172062'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy3