    {
      "id": "PopularPost371571",
      "post_content": "While I will admit that it is not too great of a card, and that it does cost more than I would like to pay, it isn't as bad as most people are pointing out.\n  \n   \nThere is a big difference between \"Whenever a creature **attacks, you** gain 1 life.\" and what others are apparently reading as \"Whenever a creature **attacks you,** gain 1 life.\"\n  \n   \nThis is not just for soaking up damage when you are on the defensive. Crank out those soldier/human/spirit tokens, start turning them sideways, and you gain life. Does that make it leaps and bounds better? No. But at least it is better that some of you are giving it, imo.\n  \n   \n2.5/5 High cost, low impact. Decent in WW or tokens that may also card about life gain. Not terrible, but not great either.\n  \n   \nEDIT: better in larger games where more creatures would have more chances to trigger this, so maybe a 3/5?",
      "posted_by": "Bbone37",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost371571\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">While I will admit that it is not too great of a card, and that it does cost more than I would like to pay, it isn't as bad as most people are pointing out. \r<br/> <br/>There is a big difference between \"Whenever a creature <b>attacks, you </b>gain 1 life.\" and what others are apparently reading as \"Whenever a creature <b>attacks you,</b> gain 1 life.\"\r<br/> <br/>This is not just for soaking up damage when you are on the defensive. Crank out those soldier/human/spirit tokens, start turning them sideways, and you gain life. Does that make it leaps and bounds better? No. But at least it is better that some of you are giving it, imo. \r<br/> <br/>2.5/5 High cost, low impact. Decent in WW or tokens that may also card about life gain. Not terrible, but not great either.\r<br/> <br/>EDIT: better in larger games where more creatures would have more chances to trigger this, so maybe a 3/5?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '371571'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy99869\">Bbone37</span>\r\n                                (4/22/2014 1:11:05 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div cla